ExchangeRatePolicy
  permission gating
    without currency_rates.manage permission
      denies all actions
    with currency_rates.manage permission
      allows index / show / create
      allows update/destroy on own-org manual row
      denies update/destroy on API row (organization_id IS NULL) — EC-05, NEG-08
      denies update/destroy on other org's manual row (defense-in-depth)
    as owner (role_enum bypass)
      allows all actions on own manual row
      still denies mutation of global API row
  Scope.resolve (NEG-04 multi-tenant isolation)
    returns global rows OR own-org rows, never other-org rows
    returns none when no current organization

